Content Acquisition Professional
Source:
Gulf News Classifieds
Date: 29-04-2014
Categories:
Media
Please see Job Details for Apply instructions
Saved!
Job Details
Vuclip provides high quality video content to over 110 million mobile users daily across the globe. We are committed to providing a high quality user experience on both high and low-end mobile devices. We require a high caliber, energetic Media Professional who can turn problems into opportunities and has an eye for detail to work in a multinational startup environment where there are challenges and opportunities to grow. POSITION: CONTENT ACQUISITION PROFESSIONAL With in-depth knowledge of the media industry and both Arabic and Western video content. Should have a minimum of 2 years experience and be an Arabic speaker. Email CV to: mai@vuclip.com
